snippet.title: Assassin's Creed Unity - Dead Kings Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Introducing Assassin’s Creed Unity Dead Kings. This exciting new campaign will let you explore the crypts of France’s fallen leaders and discover the mysteries locked within the shadowy depths.

Follow Assassin's Creed Unity at GameSpot.com!
